'''Sebuda''' ke tumelo le [[filosofi]]. E tsebega le ka leina la ''Buddha Dharma'' goba ''Dhamma'', yeo e rago ''dithuto tša yo a tsogilego'' ka maleme a [[Sanskrit]] le [[Pali]]&nbsp;(malele a dipuku tsa kgale tša ''Buddhist''). 

Sebuda e thomile ka ngwagakgolo was botshelela ke [[Gautama Buddha|Siddhartha Gautama]], yeo a bilego a bitšwa "Buddha". 

